# ~/.claude : track ONLY agents/, rules/, skills/. Ignore every other direct
# child of ~/.claude (runtime state, caches, history, sessions, plugins,
# settings.json, secrets). `.claude/*` matches one level only, so files under
# the un-ignored dirs below are kept.
.claude/*
!.claude/agents
!.claude/rules
!.claude/skills
